#. HTML: </p><h1>
#. VAR: 111. Chandappahānasutta → paṭhamachandarāgasuttaṃ (bj) | chandarāgi 1 (pts1)
msgctxt "sn22.111:0.3"
msgid "111. Chandappahānasutta "
msgstr "111. Giving Up Desire "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "sn22.111:1.1"
msgid "Sāvatthinidānaṃ. "
msgstr "At Sāvatthī. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn22.111:1.2"
msgid "“Rūpe, bhikkhave, yo chando yo rāgo yā nandī yā taṇhā, taṃ pajahatha. "
msgstr "“Mendicants, you should give up any desire, greed, relishing, and craving for form. "

msgctxt "sn22.111:1.3"
msgid "Evaṃ taṃ rūpaṃ pahīnaṃ bhavissati ucchinnamūlaṃ tālāvatthukataṃ anabhāvaṃkataṃ āyatiṃ anuppādadhammaṃ. "
msgstr "Thus that form will be given up, cut off at the root, made like a palm stump, obliterated, and unable to arise in the future. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn22.111:1.4"
msgid "Vedanāya … pe … "
msgstr "You should give up any desire, greed, relishing, and craving for feeling … "

msgctxt "sn22.111:1.5"
msgid "saññāya … "
msgstr "perception … "

msgctxt "sn22.111:1.6"
msgid "saṅkhāresu … "
msgstr "choices … "

msgctxt "sn22.111:1.7"
msgid "viññāṇe yo chando yo rāgo yā nandī yā taṇhā, taṃ pajahatha. "
msgstr "consciousness. "

msgctxt "sn22.111:1.8"
msgid "Evaṃ taṃ viññāṇaṃ pahīnaṃ bhavissati ucchinnamūlaṃ tālāvatthukataṃ anabhāvaṃkataṃ āyatiṃ anuppādadhamman”ti. "
msgstr "Thus that consciousness will be given up, cut off at the root, made like a palm stump, obliterated, and unable to arise in the future.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn22.111:1.9"
msgid "Navamaṃ. "
msgstr ""

